Assertion:
------------------------------
assertionEquals(),
assertionNotEquals(),
assertionTrue(),
AssertionFalse(),
etc..

Tagging:
------------------------------
helps to Group certian types of test together.
@Tag

10 test methods --> 4 are Sucess testmethods ,
                --> 4 are Failure testmethods ,
                --> 2 are Importatnt testmethods 
                
Create Configuration , include and exclude confuguratiob -- name of the test method .


TestSuites:
------------------------------
helps to group and run several unit test together at once multiple packages and multiple classes.

@ExcludePakages("...")
@IncludePackages("...")
@IncludeClassNamePattern("....")
@SelectClass
@SelectPackage("com.test")  -->Select the base package.
@RunWith("JunitPlatform.class") --> depricated -->@Suite



@RepeatedTest:
--------------------------------
To repeat the test a specified number of times.
@RepeatedTest
checking thread safty by running a test repeatedly -- concorance testing on methods
verification stability of the method to ensure that the test method consistency 


TestExecutionOrder:
----------------------------------
Determine the order in which the test methods are going to be executed 
@Order
@TestMehodOrder("..")


TestInterface:
----------------------------------
LifeCycle Methods -/ Test Fixture
2 things--> 1. is test fixture method , actual test methods
for more readability of the code we can exclude the test fixture to and interface and we can make the class implements the interface

@TestInstatnce(Lifecycle.PER_CLASS)

